value.title: Graham warns Biden immigration policies will lead to 'caravan after caravan' at US-Mexico border

value.title: Cruz opposes Xavier Becerra as 'absurd' Biden pick for HHS secretary: 'He's not a doctor'

value.title: Pence and Trump's relationship is 'amicable,' source says
value.excerpt: Former Vice President Mike Pence and former President Donald Trump have spoken twice since the inauguration last month, according to a knowledgeable source, who described the pair's relationship as "amicable."

value.title: Fact check: Posts falsely claim Biden gave China control of U.S. power grid
value.excerpt: No executive order signed by President Joe Biden gave China control of the U.S. power grid, and his order isn't linked to the Texas power outages.

value.title: Biden asks high court to drop two Trump-era Medicaid cases
value.excerpt: The Biden administration is asking the Supreme Court not to hear arguments in two cases on its March calendar about the Trump administration’s plan to remake Medicaid by requiring recipients to work.

value.title: 'Where is everyone?': Inside Trump's DC hotel post-presidency
value.excerpt: A sprawling lobby and bar with only a handful of people. Confused guests asking where everybody went. Elegant, but empty hallways. These are the scenes CNN observed inside the Trump International Hotel in Washington, DC, this month as the once-humming destination confronts a new reality without its namesake

value.title: Trump offered Kim Jong Un a ride home on Air Force One following Vietnam summit, source says
value.excerpt: Then-President Donald Trump in 2019 offered North Korean leader Kim Jong Un a ride home on Air Force One following their Vietnam summit, a former senior administration official who was on the trip confirmed to CNN.

value.title: John Kerry 'colluded' with Iran to undermine Trump, report says
value.excerpt: Biden administration officials, including John Kerry and Robert Malley, had meetings with Iranian Foreign Minister Javad Zarif during the Trump administration that were orchestrated to undermine President Biden's predecessor, a new report claims.

value.title: Trump: Supreme Court tax return decision a ‘continuation of the greatest political witch hunt’
value.excerpt: Former President Trump on Monday slammed the Supreme Court for declining to halt the turnover of his tax records to a New York prosecutor, calling it “a continuation of the greatest political Witch Hunt in the history of our Country.”
